 "3/4 Soothing Cream" is a lipid complex composed of barley grain, Butyrospermum Parkii and Argania Spinosa Kernel oil, in a mixture with panthenol and bisabolol.

 Investigators concure that combination of these substances in "3/4 Soothing Cream" will be efficacious non-steroidal treatment of Atopic Dermatiti ( AD).

